reviews.text: 15 Mar 19: lunch with friends here, we ordered set lunch, free-flow drinks and soup, the spaghetti is good, chicken with honey mustard sauce, but I don’t think it is honey mustard sauce, it just like a color mixture, luckily the taste is not bad. Price is around $60-80. During lunch hour, not many people come and no need to queue.
lunch, nice place, lot of choice with fair price

Welcome soft bread, unlimited soups,  various pasta dishes with rich ingredients, perfect choices of cold and hot coffee and tea, clean and calm environment at reasonable price!!! But why?? Why this restaurant is not busy and why people give only four stars here??? Whenever I came here, I shared with my friends of ideas of why.

First why was agreed by all that its enteranc was too simple and looking like a normal local 茶餐厅. Not many will recognise it is a pasta restaurant, if you don't understand Chinese.

Second why was suggested by myself, that the pasta noodle was overcooked. Cooking level of noodle is really up to individual taste. But i think al dente is a standard and mostly preferred. But its noodle is too soft and easily broken, overcooked.
Very nice staff. Good taste. Limited pasta and spagetti options. Good quantity. Nice interiors. Quiet and less crowded. Clean place. Thanks for the services.
Good.

reviews.text: Nice hotel for a reasonable price with quite a good position in the center. I loved that you could make a tea or coffee in your room cause I really need a kick in the morning. The breakfast was quite okay, even though the selection was not too great. However, we payed for it separately which was good as it only starts at 7, which was not early enough for us on some days.

Hotel Best Western Plus is (I thought) one of the finest hotel of Hong Kong.. But I was wrong.. U can easily listen to what's happening to your next room.. And they can also hear you loud and clear.. So those who want to make some noise and need privacy.. U better don't look for this one.. Staff can hardly speak English.. Staff was fine.. Helpful  sometimes.. View is good.. If you get higher floor.. 17th is on top.. Area is good.. Everything nearby..
Solid stay with helpful staff. Easy shuttle from the airport. Right in the centre of Kowloon with easy access to everything.
Good room and amenities.. Staff are helpful and housekeeping is regular.. Only wifi could be better! Enjoyed my stay at the hotel

THIS HOTEL HAS BED BUGS IN THEIR BEDS!!! BEWARE!!! GOT SOME NASTY BITES FROM IT!!! Old Hotel, Rude Staffs, Dirty Rooms, Hard bed as if you were sleeping on the floor and smelly rooms. Next time if your trainees made a mistake on our reservations just admit it and we will understand. Don't raise your voice to the guests and insist you are right which is definetly it was your staffs mistake!!! NOT COMING BACK AT THIS HOTEL EVER!!!

reviews.text:
비추... 싸게 갈려면 걍 숙박하시면 됩니다.
1. 비누없음(홍콩은 비누 안쓰나? 편의점에도 비누 안팔던데...)
2. 일회용 면도기 없음
3. 2인 1실 이용시 더블침대 하지 마세요.. 침대가 생각보다 작음
    차라리 싱글침대 2개 있는 방으로 예약하세요...
4. 전기사용 불편 : 여행용 멀티 플러그 가져 갔는데... 사용가능한 벽 콘센트는 단 하나. 이유는? 홍콩의 콘센트 type이 구멍 3개인건 아시죠? 그런데... 실제 사용하는 2개를 제외한 한개의 구명이 직사각형으로 된 콘센트도 있고 둥글게 된 콘센트도 있네요...국내 파는 멀티콘센트는 거의 직사각형. 딱 한게만 제가 가져간 멀티콘센트(직사각형)가 사용가능했습니다. 혹시나 해서 저는 T형 3구멀티탭을 가져가서 모두 사용가능했습니다.
5. 객실 및 화장실 모두 작음 => 이용불편

Nice hotel for a reasonable price with quite a good position in the center. I loved that you could make a tea or coffee in your room cause I really need a kick in the morning. The breakfast was quite okay, even though the selection was not too great. However, we payed for it separately which was good as it only starts at 7, which was not early enough for us on some days.
價格實惠，地理位置很好，附近就是機場快線的免費巴士站(百樂酒店門口)，旁邊九記和 ancle 4餐廳都便宜好吃。還有5樓以下樓層設吸煙房。

Hotel Best Western Plus is (I thought) one of the finest hotel of Hong Kong.. But I was wrong.. U can easily listen to what's happening to your next room.. And they can also hear you loud and clear.. So those who want to make some noise and need privacy.. U better don't look for this one.. Staff can hardly speak English.. Staff was fine.. Helpful  sometimes.. View is good.. If you get higher floor.. 17th is on top.. Area is good.. Everything nearby..

有夠差勁
因長榮罷工無法旅行，申請無法退費證明，打電話給客服，一直說會處理，拖2個禮拜沒處理，還說沒有這筆訂單。
